---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Careers at Lau Hairdressing | Join Our Team in Maidstone"
  description="Join the Lau Hairdressing team in Maidstone. We're recruiting experienced stylists and looking for passionate students to start their career in hairdressing."
>
  <!-- HERO BANNER -->
  <section class="careers-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="careers-hero__inner">
        <p class="careers-hero__eyebrow">We're recruiting</p>
        <h1 class="careers-hero__title">Join Our Team</h1>
        <p class="careers-hero__lead">Lau Hairdressing is recruiting experienced stylists to join our great team. Get in touch today.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="page-top">
    <!-- INTRO -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="page-title">Current Vacancies</h2>
        <h3 class="subheading">It's all about the people</h3>
        <p>Lau Hairdressing can offer you a fantastic opportunity to develop yourself as an individual, having fun with the satisfying knowledge that you are creating a real career and not just a job. So, if you're thinking about a career in this fantastic industry and want to know more about it, then email us now.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- VACANCIES GRID -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="two-col">
          <!-- Students -->
          <div class="careers-card">
            <div class="careers-card__badge">Open position</div>
            <h3 class="pricing-category">Students</h3>
            <h4 class="subheading">Our Future Professionals</h4>
            <p>We are always looking for enthusiastic people to join our team. If you are self motivated, passionate about fashion, have an artistic flair and feel ready to create your own future? Then you should consider a career with Lau Hairdressing. Don't be fooled, it's not going to be easy but it's definitely going to be worth it!</p>
            <p>Please email us in confidence to see if there are any current vacancies.</p>
            <div class="btn-group">
              <a href="/contact.html" class="btn btn--primary">Enquire</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Experienced Stylists -->
          <div class="careers-card">
            <div class="careers-card__badge">Open position</div>
            <h3 class="pricing-category">Experienced Stylists</h3>
            <h4 class="subheading">Are you an Experienced Stylist?</h4>
            <p>Do you need a new challenge with a great established company? To enquire if we have any current vacancies available, please contact our salon manager in complete confidence below with your current C.V. If not now, we may do in the very near future. We look forward to your contact.</p>
            <div class="btn-group">
              <a href="/contact.html" class="btn btn--primary">Enquire</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
